      <title>新加坡要求奢侈品卖家在洗钱丑闻后采取更多行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/singapore-demands-luxury-sellers-do-more-after-laundering-fiasco</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为该国打击洗钱举措的一部分，新加坡呼吁该国的房地产经纪人、宝石经销商和豪华汽车销售商更加主动地标记可疑客户。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/singapore-demands-luxury-sellers-do-more-after-laundering-fiasco</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
